Titolo: Boktai 2: Solar Boy Django

Anno: 2004

Descrizione: Boktai 2: Solar Boy Django, also known as Zoktai, is a video game that was developed and published by Konami for the Game Boy Advance. Released in North America and Japan in 2004 and in Europe in 2005, it is the sequel to Boktai: The Sun Is in Your Hand.
Boktai 2's game cartridge includes a photometric light sensor that measures the amount of sunlight/uv rays exposed to it.

Genere: Action role-playing 

Valutazione: N/A
